{
  "stem": "1518.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But as soon as we came to-- to the Oder, that's when they really were fighting.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "A lot of lives, when we crossed the Oder, the fields were littered with bodies like flies, the Polish Army, the Russian Army, both.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Anyway, after the Oder, already, it went fast.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, from-- from Warsaw till-- till we met with the American by the Elbe.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I think-- I think April.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "April or May, the beginning of May.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "When I met with the Americans, that was it, finished.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The war was finished.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In the battle, I was-- I was a soldier like everybody else.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The only thing, I wasn't like-- I wasn't in the-- in the-- in the front lines before the Germans-- before the-- the-- the troops came.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I wasn't there, like most of it, in the observation points, like ahead of the Army.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was always ahead of the Army.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "My-- my-- my company, always ahead.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We used to be like most of the time on observation points, like, we used to go into a village, a house right between the Germans and us.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we used to send messages, like the artillery is here, the snipers is here, radios.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Radios, they had already-- get mixed, like it's not radars, they had like to pinpoint these things.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Because on the German soil already, we were like in the communications.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I was sitting by the radio.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Like, we used to take turns, you know, and-- and I soon as I left, another he was-- he was a Ukrainian boy.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He was about maybe two years older than me.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And he was sitting by the radio, by the window a little bit bigger than this, you know.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
